<p>It's plain that this one isn't your cup of tea, so I won't belabor this much longer. In my headcanon, which you're free to disregard, it's an intelligent force at work. In the <em>article</em>, it's merely a hypothesis. The Foundation acknowledges there's no proof for such a thing. But the alternative is wholesale violation of the laws of physics. Which of course is possible in Our Anomalous Universe, but perhaps a tad less likely.</p>

